<div class="sidebar-module sidebar-module-inset alert alert-info darkblue">
    <h4><strong>About</strong></h4>
    <div class="intro-text">
        <img class="img-responsive img-circle img-thumbnail pull-left" style="width:30%;height:30%; margin-right:20px"
             src="{{ site.author.pic }}" alt="">
        <p><strong>{{ site.author.name }}</strong><br>{{ site.author.title }}</p>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <p>Hi, I am Gabi! I am a Data Engineer. What does it mean? Well, it means that I am the person
        Data Scientists work with to ensure that the data they work with is stored properly,
        retrieved effortlessly and that their large datasets have meaning.</p>

    <p> As an experienced Software Engineer, I have chosen to focus on databases (in all shapes, sizes and
        flavors!). </p>

    <p>I have very strong ties to the open source community and enjoy speaking at events and user groups around the
        world.

    <p> Are you into PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, Elasticsearch and such?
        Get in touch with me! I always look forward to learning new things and helping people with database issues.</p>
    <hr>
    <p>Passions: technology, legos (I am a proud owner of {{ site.author.lego }} pieces), HBO series and
        opensource.</p>
</div>
